{"id":1254,"date":"2020-09-11T20:09:53","date_gmt":"2020-09-11T13:09:53","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/thocaca.com\/?p=1254"},"modified":"2021-08-22T08:17:14","modified_gmt":"2021-08-22T01:17:14","slug":"nhung-linh-vat-cua-thoi-hoc-sinh","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/blog\/2020\/09\/11\/nhung-linh-vat-cua-thoi-hoc-sinh\/","title":{"rendered":"Nh\u1eefng linh v\u1eadt c\u1ee7a th\u1eddi h\u1ecdc sinh!"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Xin ch\u00e0o c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Th\u1eddi h\u1ecdc sinh, c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m, m\u00e0 \u1ea9n ch\u1ee9a trong \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n d\u00e0i, m\u00e0 n\u1ed9i dung c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang \u0111a ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec1u &#8220;c\u01b0\u1eddi ra n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft&#8221;! V\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u1ea1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi h\u1ecdc sinh, nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9 h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng nh\u01b0 r\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1eb3ng li\u00ean quan, l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng &#8220;linh v\u1eadt&#8221; b\u1ea5t h\u1ee7 m\u00e0 bi\u1ebft bao th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 h\u1ecdc sinh ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o qu\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c! Nay m\u00ecnh r\u00e3nh r\u1ed7i, n\u00ean s\u1ebd \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng linh v\u1eadt huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ec3 ai trong ch\u00fang ta, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng tr\u1ea3i qua th\u1eddi h\u1ecdc sinh &#8220;m\u00e1u l\u1eeda&#8221; , khi nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i s\u1ebd m\u1ec9m c\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00ec ch\u00fang \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng r\u1ea5t g\u00ec v\u00e0 n\u00e0y n\u1ecd \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang ta!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>1. Th\u1ea7n xo\u00e0i<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"658\" height=\"586\" src=\"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/2954314317567482510571071022300657098424320n-15288595313631828141175-15288609206141257248658-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1256\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/2954314317567482510571071022300657098424320n-15288595313631828141175-15288609206141257248658-1.png 658w, https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/2954314317567482510571071022300657098424320n-15288595313631828141175-15288609206141257248658-1-300x267.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 658px) 100vw, 658px\" \/><figcaption>Th\u1ea7n xo\u00e0i trong truy\u1ec1n thuy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e2y \u1ea1!<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Ch\u1eb3ng bi\u1ebft n\u00f3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb bao gi\u1edd, c\u01a1 m\u00e0 c\u1ee9 m\u1ed7i d\u1ecbp m\u00f9a thi l\u00e0 n\u00f3 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c share nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i b\u00f9a ch\u00fa c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh phi th\u01b0\u1eddng. Gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi share kh\u00f4ng \u00f4n c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed7, tr\u00fang t\u1ee7, ng\u1ed3i g\u1ea7n th\u1eb1ng h\u1ecdc gi\u1ecfi,&#8230; Kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u nghi\u1ec7m kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng m\u00e0 nh\u00ecn qu\u1ea3 xo\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y \u1ee9a n\u01b0\u1edbc mi\u1ebfng ra r\u1ed3i ^^<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Theo m\u00ecnh th\u00ec ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c linh v\u1eadt n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb h\u1ed9i sinh vi\u00ean ch\u1ee9 ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc sinh. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ed5 th\u00f4ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc l\u00e0 c\u00e2y c\u1ed1i trong khu\u00f4n vi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1eddng. \u1ede tr\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ed5 th\u00f4ng th\u00ec \u0111a ph\u1ea7n to\u00e0n l\u00e0 x\u00e0 c\u1eeb, ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, b\u1eb1ng l\u0103ng, hoa s\u1eefa,&#8230; Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc th\u00ec l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u&#8230; xo\u00e0i. V\u00e0 m\u00f9a n\u00f3 ra qu\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0o m\u00f9a thi. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean t\u1ef1 d\u01b0ng n\u00f3 b\u1ed9c ph\u00e1t tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9 g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi m\u00f9a thi, d\u1ea7n gi\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh linh v\u1eadt c\u1ee7a m\u1ea5y anh ch\u1ecb sinh vi\u00ean. C\u00e1c em h\u1ecdc sinh b\u1eaft tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00f4i \u00e0!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>2. Th\u1ea7n th\u00eca<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"933\" src=\"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/cac-si-tu-dem-thia-vao-phong-thi-de-de-lay-may-3d4c9c.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1257\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/cac-si-tu-dem-thia-vao-phong-thi-de-de-lay-may-3d4c9c.jpg 700w, https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/cac-si-tu-dem-thia-vao-phong-thi-de-de-lay-may-3d4c9c-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><figcaption>\u0110i thi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u1ea3i mang theo th\u1ea7n th\u00eca nha!<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi th\u1ea7n xo\u00e0i th\u00ec th\u1ea7n th\u00eca c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111a s\u1ed1 h\u1ecdc sinh xem l\u00e0 linh v\u1eadt h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a thi. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea7n th\u00eca c\u00f3 v\u1ebb s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh k\u00e9m h\u01a1n th\u1ea7n xo\u00e0i th\u00ec ph\u1ea3i. V\u00ec \u0111a ph\u1ea7n to\u00e0n th\u1ea5y m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi share v\u1edbi n\u1ed9i dung l\u00e0: &#8220;Share th\u1ea7n th\u00eca \u0111\u1ec3 qua m\u00f4n&#8221; ^^<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>3. C\u1ecf ba l\u00e1<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/avtcobala-1556291893-504-width640height480_schema_article-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1258\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/avtcobala-1556291893-504-width640height480_schema_article-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/avtcobala-1556291893-504-width640height480_schema_article-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/avtcobala-1556291893-504-width640height480_schema_article-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/avtcobala-1556291893-504-width640height480_schema_article-678x381.jpg 678w, https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/avtcobala-1556291893-504-width640height480_schema_article.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption>C\u1ecf ba l\u00e1 li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 may m\u1eafn!<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Theo quan ni\u1ec7m d\u00e2n gian th\u00ec c\u1ecf ba l\u00e1 l\u00e0 lo\u00e0i c\u00e2y mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 may m\u1eafn. V\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u00f4 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua n\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ed3i. C\u01a1 m\u00e0 c\u00e1i c\u1ecf ba l\u00e1 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf h\u01a1n l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n th\u00eca hay th\u1ea7n xo\u00e0i. V\u00ec n\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 mang l\u1ea1i may m\u1eafn, ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c &#8220;kh\u00f4ng h\u1ecdc \u0111i\u1ec3m cao&#8221; hay &#8220;kh\u00f4ng h\u1ecdc m\u00e0 v\u1eabn qua m\u00f4n&#8221; nh\u01b0 2 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7n ph\u00eda tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2u!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>4. Qu\u1ea1t tr\u1ea7n r\u01a1i<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" src=\"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/quat-tran-bi-roi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1259\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/quat-tran-bi-roi.jpg 500w, https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/quat-tran-bi-roi-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/quat-tran-bi-roi-326x245.jpg 326w, https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/quat-tran-bi-roi-80x60.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><figcaption>N\u1ed7i khi\u1ebfp s\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a bi\u1ebft bao th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 h\u1ecdc sinh, sinh vi\u00ean Vi\u1ec7t Nam!<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ecbnh m\u1ec7nh ch\u1ee9 h\u1ed3i m\u00ecnh \u0111i h\u1ecdc, m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1i qu\u1ea1t tr\u1ea7n r\u01a1i v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u, r\u1ed3i m\u00ecnh t\u1ef1 huy\u1ec5n ra c\u1ea3nh m\u00e1u ch\u1ea3y, \u0111\u1ea7u r\u01a1i. C\u1eaft \u0111\u1ee9t phay \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ee9a m\u00ecnh gh\u00e9t. C\u01a1 m\u00e0 s\u1ed1 h\u00ean, su\u1ed1t 12 n\u0103m \u0111i h\u1ecdc ph\u1ed5 th\u00f4ng v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n 6 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc, m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u1ea3nh kinh ho\u00e0ng \u1ea5y.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf v\u1eadt ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng t\u1eeb l\u00e2u, th\u00ec v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 qu\u1ea1t tr\u1ea7n c\u0169ng ngang gi\u1ea3i l\u1eafm. T\u1eeb quay ch\u1eadm nh\u01b0 r\u00f9a b\u00f2, th\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1eadt c\u00f2n h\u01a1n. Cho \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eeba quay v\u1eeba ph\u00e1t ra ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n \u1ea7m \u0129. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec9nh \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0 v\u1eeba quay v\u1eeba rung l\u1eafc. L\u1eafc nh\u01b0 m\u1ea5y em ch\u00e2n d\u00e0i trong bar \u1ea5y. Ng\u00fang ngu\u1ea9y khi\u1ebfn bao t\u00e2m h\u1ed3n con tr\u1ebb tr\u1edf n\u00ean ho\u1ea3ng s\u1ee3! \ud83d\ude00<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>5. R\u1ebb lau b\u1ea3ng<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"660\" height=\"495\" src=\"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/nguyen-ha-trang-1522034359028309600309.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1260\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/nguyen-ha-trang-1522034359028309600309.jpg 660w, https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/nguyen-ha-trang-1522034359028309600309-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/nguyen-ha-trang-1522034359028309600309-326x245.jpg 326w, https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/nguyen-ha-trang-1522034359028309600309-80x60.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\" \/><figcaption>Chi\u1ebfc r\u1ebb lau b\u1ea3ng c\u00f2n n\u00e1t h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi ch\u1ecb D\u1eadu \ud83d\ude41<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u00e1i linh v\u1eadt h\u01a1i b\u1ea9n b\u1ea9n n\u00e0y th\u00ec m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng xin c\u00fai r\u1ea1p ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1 l\u1ec5. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng cho nh\u1eefng g\u00ec kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 h\u1ecdc sinh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua tr\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc. Chi\u1ebfn tranh \u0111i qua \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0ng m\u1ea1c ti\u00eau \u0111i\u1ec1u, nh\u00e0 c\u1eeda x\u01a1 x\u00e1c. Th\u00ec n\u0103m h\u1ecdc \u0111i qua, \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i c\u00e1i r\u1ebb lau b\u1ea3ng n\u00e1t h\u01a1n cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi ch\u1ecb D\u1eadu. Th\u1eadt l\u00e0 ^^<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y m\u00ecnh li\u1ec7t k\u00ea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 linh v\u1eadt n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng trong gi\u1edbi h\u1ecdc sinh, kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft n\u01a1i b\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f2n x\u1ebfp nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9 g\u00ec v\u00e0o h\u00e0ng linh v\u1eadt n\u1eefa kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ec9? N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 th\u00ec inbox cho m\u00ecnh ngay \u0111\u1ec3 m\u00ecnh s\u1eeda nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Th\u00e2n \u00e1i!<\/p>\n<!-- AddThis Advanced Settings generic via filter on the_content --><!-- AddThis Share Buttons generic via filter on the_content -->","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<div class=\"mh-excerpt\"><p>Xin ch\u00e0o c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n! Th\u1eddi h\u1ecdc sinh, c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m, m\u00e0 \u1ea9n ch\u1ee9a trong \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n d\u00e0i, m\u00e0 n\u1ed9i <a class=\"mh-excerpt-more\" href=\"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/blog\/2020\/09\/11\/nhung-linh-vat-cua-thoi-hoc-sinh\/\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng linh v\u1eadt c\u1ee7a th\u1eddi h\u1ecdc sinh!\">[&#8230;]<\/a><!-- AddThis Advanced Settings generic via filter on get_the_excerpt --><!-- AddThis Share Buttons generic via filter on get_the_excerpt --><\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1255,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[8],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1254"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1254"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1254\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1263,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1254\/revisions\/1263"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1255"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1254"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1254"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=1254"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}